>\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"082f8490b74e3a976b7892df896d000a6af02455","tid":1356040,"uid":104161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2710856eedaed83bfe8282bd046c6e1e8316dc13","tid":1356040,"uid":199709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73d59cebbeca890fda9cd1ec57544bf8bd3c465d","tid":1356040,"uid":141516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:03:44.000Z","msg":"係呀！我地比人轉哂focus，五大訴求冇人講，727冇人提，西環嗰邊咁撚大鑊都冇人屌，扔tear gas 之後開槍啊！你估打isis啊！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>上環Video 整合 (粗略) (keep updating) </strong> 元朗有夠多片 我就淨係推上環喇<br />\n麻煩各位巴絲幫手backup <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1209367\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1209367</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348465/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348209/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1350647/page/1</a> <br />\n(最新片段) 尋晚警犬無舉旗下連開四槍以上 <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/349470836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F349470836&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=6dbf03cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/349470836</a><br />\n721 上環發生了什麼事？ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3D2bX6CKzg_5w&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=206cffb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=2bX6CKzg_5w</a><br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ef1c14a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=da32fc30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=08c2c2a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=445cf016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=0ceac6d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=6ff2c42a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=2f7531d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=4906c2c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=10b21d52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=0ecf2ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=d4d1ecfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=943e39d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ea8b4e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=7e421822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=cf2accc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=ae0f9152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場 <a href=\"https://www.youtub